ğŸ› ï¸ API Setup:
--------------
1. Sign up at: https://openweathermap.org
2. Get your FREE API Key.
3. Use this endpoint to fetch weather by city name:

   https://api.openweathermap.org/data/2.5/weather?q={city}&appid={API_KEY}&units=metric

